# TimeoutRoulette

Small chat game of timeout roulette.
It got singleplayer, duel and multiplayer games. Multiplayer versions got two mods: normal and knockout, where game ends when someone "eats the bullet".

## Tutorial
[![Tutorial](TSO.Roulette_thumbnail.png)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SP0VkEmmbpQ&)

## Install
Video tutorial is for older version, but logic of the game is still the same.
To install, grab .sb file or code import below and put it into import dialog window in Streamer.Bot.

All configs are stored in the separate actions in the separate group.

You can change durations and texts of the game to your liking, or language.

Game can be started from chat commands on Twitch or YouTube and from channel point reward on Twitch.
